metadata.name: The Walk of Smilesss: Menji
metadata.description:
A clash of Menjiâ€™s world and the Smilesssvrs.

In this piece, Menji is taking a walk within the Smilesssvrs.

While walking In the Smilesssvrs, Menji had made new friends and was allowed to be himself to the fullest.

While walking further, life had sprouted and the environment had completely changed.

This all started with one step.

This step was realizing that everyone contains an abundant amount of gifts within. Once you have this awareness, the only next thing to do is share as many as you can with the world.

In exchange, the world will give you an abundant amount of Smilesss.

::)
